          | I'm an all-around techie with a past in software, ocean engineering, and international development. I&apos;m currently working to revolutionize manufacturing through accessible technology at 
          a(href='https://tulip.co') Tulip
          | .
        p
          | This site is in its early stages, but will become a collection of 
          a(href='#reading-list') writing/media I'd recommend
          | , 
          a(href='#stuff-i-like') stuff I like
          | , and 
          a(href='#projects') projects I've worked on
          |. If you have recommendations or questions, feel free to 
          a(href='mailto:carrus.justin@gmail.com') reach out
          | .
      h2#reading-list Reading List
      div
        include reading-list.pug
      h2#stuff-i-like Stuff I Like
      div
        include stuff-i-like.pug
      h2#projects Projects
      div
        include projects.pug
